{"tid":1716420,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"工程撚睇法 你敢堅持兩年 政府一定輸","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:41:39.000Z","uid":73492,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4bbb68ef9dd16b1d9fdc7743c65863985b546c30","tid":1716420,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"好現實地 香港所有行業都圍繞緊租金同樓價去思考<br />\n餐飲業 零售業 專業 所有行業 乜都好<br />\n係香港 講到尾 就係交到租金 再諗賺錢<br />\n<br />\n而每一份租約都係用一「期」做期限<br />\n一期就係三年<br />\n<br />\n而續唔續約既時期 往往係租約前半年至一年諗<br />\n<br />\n即係話 你日日/隔日/不定時玩開花<br />\n商家佬最後一年埋單 係蝕多過賺<br />\n佢就唔會續鋪 到時香港產業就完<br />\n<br />\n我話知你專業 起樓工程測量 會計法律<br />\n定係服務業 飲食 物流 零售 甚至保安<br />\n都再無需求 <br />\n到時一定政府重組 香港re game <br />\n民主雙普選有硬 建國都唔一定 睇民主意向<br />\n並且連帶其他訴求都一定做到<br />\n<br />\n問題係 香港人有無呢個心 肯做多兩年？<br />\n仲要中產人士都re game 夠唔夠膽？"},{"pid":"d4d1c199d96dbed6c0036e13e4125aceee99712f","tid":1716420,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:41:06.000Z","msg":"維穩費燒曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924aaa72f64ff4bb9619a1b3a443a7b4a0e6d5e2","tid":1716420,"uid":7855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"最難既的確係堅持<br />\n亦要守<br />\n亦要三罷攻<br />\n不定時"},{"pid":"080684ae72a122aa1c6cd6194ac4dc8a55290542","tid":1716420,"uid":73492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17983120880d8517f9a8fbad16fc43616b9cf1c6","tid":1716420,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"香港人！堅持！"}]}